name: Magic City Acceptance Center
directions: The building is located on the corner of 4th Avenue South and 25th Street South. Enter through double glass doors in the rear parking lot. The Magic City Acceptance Center is on the left side of the building and has an all gender restroom. There is also an all gender restroom in the main lobby.
comment: The Magic City Acceptance Center is a safe, affirming space for LGBTQ folks ages 13-24. Super open and affirming. Stop by sometime!
